{"word":"G568 - ἀπέχω - apéchō - ap-ekh'-o - Be","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπέχω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apéchō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ekh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - போதும்"},{"paragraph":"it is enough, sufficient"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G2192 - ἔχω - échō - ekh'-o/2192\">G2192</a>; (active) to <i>have out</i>, that is, <i>receive in full</i>; (intransitive) to <i>keep</i> (oneself) <i>away</i>, that is, <i>be distant</i> (literally or figuratively): - be, have, receive.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1777/1777\">G1777</a>, <a href=\"#/G2192/2192\">G2192</a>, <a href=\"#/G2722/2722\">G2722</a>, <a href=\"#/G3348/3348\">G3348</a>, <a href=\"#/G3353/3353\">G3353</a>, <a href=\"#/G472/472\">G472</a>, <a href=\"#/G568/568\">G568</a>"}]}